==早年生活==
阿伯特出生于[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[阿斯伯里帕克|阿斯伯里帕克]]的一个[[演藝界|演藝界]][[家庭|家庭]]。他的父母在[[玲玲馬戲團|玲玲馬戲團]]工作。<ref name=http://www.biography.com/people/bud-abbott-20617237>{{Cite web |url=http://www.biography.com/people/bud-abbott-20617237 |title=Bud Abbott Biography |accessdate=2014-08-06 |archive-date=2014-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416010955/http://www.biography.com/people/bud-abbott-20617237 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=James Robert Parish, William T. Leonard|title=The funsters|year=1979|publisher=Arlington House|isbn=9780870004186|pages=12|url=http://books.google.ca/books?id=Zn1ZAAAAMAAJ&q=%22William+%22Bud%22+Abbott+was+born+on+Wednesday,+October+2,+1895,+in+Asbury+Park,+New+Jersey.%22&dq=%22William+%22Bud%22+Abbott+was+born+on+Wednesday,+October+2,+1895,+in+Asbury+Park,+New+Jersey.%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=hR1TU8S3IYGP2gWFpYHgBw&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAA}}</ref>阿伯特在还是孩子时就辍学并开始在[[康尼島|康尼島]]为父亲工作。后来，阿伯特开始安排滑稽戏表演之旅。但是在15岁的时候，阿伯特被麻醉诱骗到一艘开往挪威的船上，他最终以工作的方式回到美国，并在回归后搬到底特律。<ref name=http://www.biography.com/people/bud-abbott-20617237 />

==个人生活==
